data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Trussville! This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a host of desirable features. The spacious and inviting layout includes a large eat-in kitchen, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends.  On the main level, you'll find the luxurious primary suite with its own ensuite bathroom, providing a private retreat for relaxation. Upstairs the well-appointed bedrooms offer ample space and natural light, creating a comfortable and cozy atmosphere.  Step outside to discover the expansive backyard, a perfect oasis for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day. The property's prime location ensures convenience, being close to all things Trussville, including shopping, dining, and recreational amenities.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home – schedule a viewing today and experience the charm and comfort of living in this delightful Trussville residence!
